        All first invasive breast cancer cases from a National Cancer Registry&#xD;
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
        All women with stage I-III disease who survived at least 12 months post-diagnosis&#xD;
&#xD;
        Exclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
        Unknown cause of death Treatment outside the region (thus precluding the treatment&#xD;
        assessment)&#xD;
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
